query:
SELECT c.id, c.contractNumber, c.requestId, c.projectId, c.status, r.id as req_id, r.currentStage 
FROM contracts_enhanced c 
LEFT JOIN mosque_requests r ON c.requestId = r.id 
ORDER BY c.id DESC LIMIT 5;
